<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language>英文</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 09:14:45 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix may soon livestream a golf tournament featuring F1 drivers and pro golfers]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您从未想过 Formula 1 和职业高尔夫可以并存，那么 Netflix 不敢苟同。据<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASRtuQblkvRfIH8NEkV7PIZnQH2NswdR_ip-kttjPH21&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fnetflix-plans-first-live-streamed-sports-event-with-celebrity-golf-tournament-cd76c2c1%3Fmod%3DdjemalertNEWS"><em>《华尔街日报》</em></a>报道，流媒体服务据说正在洽谈直播其首个体育赛事，这是一场由 F1 车手和职业高尔夫球手参加的名人高尔夫锦标赛。据报道，它将以<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Netflix;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2a170a1e-7e5c-4edd-b5dd-ea6d3bd9416a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Netflix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIyYTE3MGExZS03ZTVjLTRlZGQtYjVkZC1lYTZkM2JkOTQxNmEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmV0ZmxpeC5jb20vdHVkdW0vZnVsbC1zd2luZyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNGQzMTc0ZWUtZDE3Yy00MjEzLWE4ZmMtMmFjMDNiMWVjY2Y1In0&amp;signature=AQAAAbDyYfao--nJtJit0KcpW2oH7i4HcD_cG74XQStxZZRL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Ffull-swing"><em>Full Swing</em></a>和<em>&nbsp;</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-formula-1-drive-to-survive-season-five-premiere-date-211056959.html"><em>Drive to Survive</em></a> ，Netflix 纪录片，关注 F1 车手和职业高尔夫球手。据<em>《华尔街日报》</em>报道，谈判仍处于初步阶段。</p><p>名人高尔夫赛事将是 Netflix 制定格式并解决未来体育赛事直播中可能出现的任何技术问题的一种低风险方式。它以<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-cancels-second-ever-livestream-after-love-is-blind-reunion-hit-by-technical-issues-120930605.html">搞砸了</a><em>Love is Blind</em>真人秀的直播而闻名，技术问题导致长达一个小时的中断——尽管它的第一个直播活动，克里斯洛克喜剧特别节目，进行得很顺利。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该公司可能还注意到<em>Rick Shiels</em>和<em>Bob Does Sports</em>等高尔夫 YouTube 频道的流行。这些比赛通常以像<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://youtu.be/ofDGxMrSNZ0">Max Homa</a>这样的顶级职业选手为特色，他们打球并与普通球员竞争，像我们其他人打高尔夫球时一样说垃圾话和咒骂。类似的形式，F1 车手和球员在比赛的同时也享受乐趣，可能会吸引平时不会看高尔夫的普通观众—— <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/obsessed/netflix-full-swing-how-a-show-about-golf-won-real-housewives-fans">就像<em>Full Swing</em>所做的那样</a>。</p><p>一年多来，Netflix 一直在探索直播体育流媒体。它之前曾竞标过一级方程式的美国直播权，但据报道输给了 ESPN。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASzDCoXPlZXQpPKc4eaNGG4-2ZF6-C8AfG2Kg6Muqh-j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fnetflix-explores-investing-in-sports-leagues-bidding-on-streaming-rights-11667930861">据推测</a>，它还探索了网球、自行车和其他低调运动的权利竞标。</p><p>今年早些时候，联席 CEO 泰德·萨兰多斯 (Ted Sarandos) 表示“我们不是反体育，我们是营利性的”，暗示 Netflix 认为体育转播权的成本在经济上没有意义。与此同时，他表示公司将保留这种可能性。与此同时，亚马逊 Prime Video 等竞争对手多年来一直在直播美国国家橄榄球联盟<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-video-nfl-black-friday-game-date-211050980.html">(NFL)</a> 、美国职业棒球大联盟 ( <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/prime-video-will-air-21-exclusive-yankees-games-in-four-states-205356250.html">Major League Baseball</a> )、ATP、 <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-07-amazon-prime-premier-league-football-uk.html">英超联赛</a>等联盟的体育赛事。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/netflix-may-soon-livestream-a-golf-tournament-featuring-f1-drivers-and-pro-golfers-091445042.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflix-may-soon-livestream-a-golf-tournament-featuring-f1-drivers-and-pro-golfers-091445042.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4d3174ee-d17c-4213-a8fc-2ac03b1eccf5</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 09:14:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686649290</ingested><modified> 2023-06-13T09:41:34+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Golf]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="3286" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7ecfed60-09c4-11ee-aec7-a9c9375b918d" width="4929"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3286" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7ecfed60-09c4-11ee-aec7