Fw?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023"><em>在这里</em></a><em>了解夏季游戏节的所有新闻</em><em>！</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/ace-attorney-games-with-apollo-justice-are-coming-to-newer-consoles-in-early-2024-070034630.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/ace-attorney-games-with-apollo-justice-are-coming-to-newer-consoles-in-early-2024-070034630.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 88c6e766-4580-444a-8e21-1c2ccb6b84c1</guid><dc:creator>玛丽拉月亮</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 07:00:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686640709</ingested><modified> 2023-06-13T07:18:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1003" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7ec6f1e0-09b2-11ee-bf7c-ae4599150854" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1003" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7ec6f1e0-09b2-11ee-bf7c-ae4599150854" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Capcom]]></me