了解——它甚至还没有发布日期——但你可以在下面的视频中观看它的预告片。 </p><div id="feeb60bedffa486f96152fff70221c5d"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4EamjuZSXJk?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023"><em>在这里</em></a><em>了解夏季游戏节的所有新闻</em><em>！</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/capcoms-kunitsu-gami-path-of-the-goddess-is-an-action-game-with-traditional-japanese-aesthetics-054801136.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/capcoms-kunitsu-gami-path-of-the-goddess-is-an-action-game-with-traditional-japanese-aesthetics-054801136.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5efa50bb-b8c1-42fd-8090-a4f7e2dc157a</guid><dc:creator>玛丽拉月亮</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 05:48:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686640770</ingested><modified> 2023-06-13T07:19:33+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1026" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7d1f6f50-09a5-11ee-abee-33232bf81cfe" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1026" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7d1f6f50-09a5-11ee-abee-33232bf81cfe" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Capcom]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A screenshot of the game 'Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess' showing a character posing with his sword and four enemies surrounded by light before they're defeated.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Kunitsu-Gami]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Capcom's Pragmata has been delayed for a second time]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>您很有可能已经完全忘记了<em>Pragmata</em> ，这是 Capcom 怪诞的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/PRAGMATAgame/status/1271196457626767360">反乌托邦科幻冒险游戏</a>。现在，Capcom 给你一个机会再次忘记它：游戏的新预告片显示该游戏将错过 2023 年的发布窗口。</p><p> “怀着沉重的心情，我们必须进一步推迟<em>Pragmata</em>的发布，”开发团队在游戏新预告片的结尾写道。 “我们的团队目前正在努力制作我们可能做的最好的游戏，但我们需要更多时间。” </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="1cbc093377d645d0a3a42d7f31b2b096"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h4Q7Q8e3M0A?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>正如消息所暗示的那样，这实际上是<em>Pragmata 的</em>发布第二次被推迟。 <em>Pragmata</em><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/PRAGMATAgame/status/1271196457626767360">于 2020 年首次宣布</a>，被一部电影预告片取笑，预告片显示一名士兵和一名年轻女孩在登上月球表面之前探索一座废弃的城市。最初的预告片暗示了反乌托邦的未来和主角之间的亲密关系，但除此之外别无其他。大约一年后，Capcom 发布了一段视频，内容是这位年轻女孩<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/PRAGMATAgame/status/1271427028768526338">为游戏的延迟道歉</a>。今年的预告片类似，但至少展示了一些游戏玩法。</p><p>现在我们知道这个年轻的女孩名叫戴安娜，她似乎受到了她那位身披重甲的朋友的保护。我们一起看到他们与类似机器人的生物战斗，探索未来派环境并组队进行高速骑乘。虽然士兵在预告片中完成了两人的大部分战斗，但它也揭示了戴安娜具有特殊能力。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/3acd8c70-097f-11ee-acec-75d6ee3beebb" style="height:1914px;width:3456px;" alt="Capcom 的科幻游戏已被推迟。" data-uuid="0e1dc08c-ff3f-32d2-b1de-09a0f9f3ec66"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">卡普空</div></figure><p>那些权力是什么？这两个角色在月球上做什么？其余的人类怎么了？这些问题将不得不等待。 <em>Pragmata</em>团队没有为游戏设置新的发布窗口，而是承诺会尽最大努力“确保最终产品是一款值得您耐心等待的产品”。</p><p> <em>Pragmata</em>计划在 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X 和 PC 游戏平台上发布。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/capcoms-pragmata-has-been-delayed-for-a-second-time-002035406.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/capcoms-pragmata-has-been-delayed-for-a-second-time-002035406.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e651361b-352a-4080-81f9-3c490a2375f4</guid><dc:creator>肖恩·巴克利</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 00:20:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686615630</ingested><modified> 2023-06-13T00:20:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sean Buckley]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/a3947990-097e-11ee-afdf-586d1dde44e3" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/a3947990-097e-11ee-afdf-586d1dde44e3" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Capcom]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[C